description: Russia Ukraine crisis news LIVE Updates: Russian President Vladimir Putin on Monday signed a decree in Moscow recognising the independence of Donetsk and Luhansk regions in eastern Ukraine. Reacting to it, US President Joe Biden signed an executive order to prohibit trade and investment between US individuals. The UK has also threatened 'significant sanctions' against Russia. Stay tuned at IndiaToday.in for Russia-Ukraine crisis news LIVE Updates.
